data.description: Very well taken care of home on a quiet cul-de-sac in the Cherry Creek School District. Your buyers will love this home and the convenience of being just around the corner from Flanders Park. This home features 3 bedrooms and one full bathroom all on one level. Spacious den on the lower level includes a fireplace and has sliding glass doors that open up to a large deck & well-maintained backyard!! Newer roof, A/C, Furnace, and Water heater. Easy access to E-470 Close to restaurants and grocery stores. Seller needs to find a replacement home. Asking for a 45-50 day closing to give time to find a new home or a 30-day rent back. Please adhere to all COVID guidelines. There is not a for sale sign at the property.
